# Password Generator Web Application

## Description

Password Generator Web Application is a lightweight client-side web application developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

The application enables users to generate secure and customizable passwords based on selected criteria, including password length, uppercase letters, lowercase letters, numbers, and special characters.

Designed with simplicity and usability in mind, the project demonstrates core front-end development concepts such as DOM manipulation, event handling, form controls, and random password generation.

## Technologies

The project was developed using the following technologies:

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (Vanilla JavaScript)

## Features

### Custom Password Length

* Generate passwords between 4 and 32 characters
* User-defined password length selection
* Dynamic password creation

### Character Selection Options

Users can include:

* Uppercase Letters (A-Z)
* Lowercase Letters (a-z)
* Numbers (0-9)
* Special Symbols (!@#$%^&*)

### Random Password Generation

* Secure randomized character selection
* Dynamic character pool generation
* Instant password creation

### User-Friendly Interface

* Simple and intuitive design
* Checkbox-based configuration
* Real-time password display

### Input Validation

* Prevents password generation when no character type is selected
* Displays user-friendly warning messages
* Ensures valid password generation criteria

## Technologies Demonstrated

This project showcases practical implementation of:

* DOM Manipulation
* Event Handling
* Conditional Logic
* Loops and Iteration
* Random Number Generation
* User Input Processing
* Front-End Web Development Fundamentals

